- ["Introducing an Austrian Backpack in Spain"](https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s13209-022-00263-x), *SERIEs* 13, p. 513–556 (2022), with [Julián Diáz-Saavedra](http://www.ugr.es/~julianalbertodiaz/) and [Ramon Marimon](https://www.ramonmarimon.eu/)

